<br>
Innate lure 1:  2% more chance to land a nuke<br>
Innate lure 2:  5% more chance to land a nuke <br>
Innate lure 3:  10% more chance to land a nuke<br>
<br>
Disintegrate:<br>
<br>
Like the spell disintegrate but for mobs up to lvl 65. no xp no loot no corpse no flagged  mobs ( i.e. they can flag mobs they don’t think we should kill outright eg old world names etc)<br>
